Requirements:
- Python 3.0 or higher
- Internet access

Installation guide:
    1) Install pip and pipenv (only for python 3.3 or lower)
        follow: https://pip.pypa.io/en/stable/installing/
        and then execute:
        >  pip install pipenv

    2) Install CherryPy
        > pip install cherrypy

        This might require you to install dependancies, install them as well.

    3) Install Requests
        > pipenv install requests

    4) Clone Lite-SSLstrip source code
        > git clone https://github.com/YorMeij/lite-sslstrip.git

    5) Execute the program
    > sudo python main.py macAlice ipAlice macBob ipBob macMallory ipMallory

Happy hacking!
